\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Cs::3>Evan<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 <$Scr_Cs::4>:<!$Scr_Cs::4>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why not?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Cs::3>Sarah:<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93We Just can\u8217\'92t!\u8221\'94}{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 <$Scr_Cs::4> }
\par\plain {\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 [ Evan looks longingly, deep into Sarah's eyes. ]<!$Scr_Cs::4>}
\par\plain {\f4\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Cs::3>Evan <!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 <$Scr_Cs::4>(softly, gently):<!$Scr_Cs::4>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I'll stop if you can look me in the eyes and tell me you don't love me anymore.\u8221\'94}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f7\fs26\b0\i0 <$Scr_Cs::4><$Scr_Ps::5>Evan's gaze weakened Sarah's resolve. She did still love him. She remained silent and relented as Evan leaned in, their kissing becoming even more passionate. However, in the midst of her passion fear struck and uncharacteristically, tears began to flow. She pulled away from Evan. She hurriedly made attempts to tuck her blouse back in<!$Scr_Cs::4><!$Scr_Ps::5>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 <$Scr_Cs::3>Sarah<!$Scr_Cs::3>}{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf8 <$Scr_Cs::4> (Frantic):<!$Scr_Cs::4>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I promised myself this wasn\u8217\'92t going to happen. I can\u8217\'92t do this, Evan, I\u8217\'92m sorry.\u8221\'94}
